Custom manufacturer of seed storage and conveying equipment. Other products include receivers, shelling equipment, and conditioning equipment. Types of seed storage equipment includes pallet boxes, magnetic separators, letdown ladders, bin outlet gates, and cob bins. Types of conveyors include belt, shuttle, and bag handling. Types of receivers include dump doors, end-mounted double lids, side unloading truck dumpers, vibratory bins, and lateral drive kits. Conditioning equipment includes structural steel frames, bin systems, access manhole doors, rebag systems, overhead bulk scales, dust filter units, hoppers, transitions, and valves. Custom capabilities include steel fabrication, aluminum and steel welding, shearing, bending, and punching. Manufacturer of laboratory equipment and cleaning equipment. Design and installation of automation equipment and control panels.
